they were pennies all right 700000 of 
them in all but they didnt come from heaven they were a 
retirement present to the rev joseph ryan from youngsters at his 
parish grade school 
the pennies came in plastic water jugs wrapped in christmas paper 
and were presented to the 70yearold priest on wednesday 
i didnt take it to the bank ryan said one of those water 
jugs weighs 200 pounds theyll have to get a truck 
the fifthgrade class at infant jesus of prague elementary school 
in this chicago suburb collected the pennies as a mathematics 
