training mission and approaching for a landing at the royal air 
force base in alconbury when the crash occurred said an air force 
spokesman 
it was the second crash of a twinengine thunderbolt jet in 
europe in two weeks a third a10 crashed on dec 8 in tracy ariz 
cavouti was being held for observation at a military hospital 
his jet crashed several miles west of this central english village 
and about 60 miles north of london said the spokesman speaking on 
condition of anonymity 
witnesses said it appeared the pilot was trying to miss this 
village and hit the open field 
