england and persuade the exbeatle to sing on the record 
one of the first guys i thought of was ringo willner said 
i remembered goodnight from the beatles white album its 
not a conventional singing voice but it works 
oconnors appearance on stay awake mary poppins came 
about when willner visited dublin at the end of 1987 
i saw her on television and i went aaaah i thought boy 
would that be great if she could do prince will come 
and to willners surprise oconnor readily agreed completing an 
