japanese banks early next year in a bid to increase the number of 
participants 
asked about estimates that he hopes to raise as much as onethird 
of the total bank loan in japan or about 5 billion kravis said 
kkr had not decided on a division of financing 
in recent weeks japanese newspapers have reported that the 
